{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"aea668e6de","title":"林彪关于各地抢枪事件给毛泽东的信（大意）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2745c0e7fd","index":0,"year":1967,"month":7,"day":0,"articleId":"aea668e6de","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"林彪","id":"44b4a39710","type":"人物"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[{"id":"e0470b1283","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aea668e6de","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"来源：《林彪元帅文集》（下册），香港凤凰书品， 2016年。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7f5cb4d02c","type":"title","text":"林彪关于各地抢枪事件给毛泽东的信（大意）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aea668e6de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4c465fcd5f","type":"paragraph","text":"武汉事件后，急待处理的一些问题正在处理。对于陈再道等人的问题，已按（毛）主席批示的方针办。……当前的问题仍然是两派对立，武斗升级；特别是少数群众组织抢夺部队枪支的事，已在南方一些省发生，情况比较严重。因此急需采取一些严厉措施等……","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aea668e6de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05d397387f","type":"paragraph","text":"1，毛泽东批示：对于群众抢枪的事，不必看得过于严重。所谓群众抢枪，有些地方实际上是部队向他们所支持的一派发枪。因此，对此事的处理似可不急，待时机成熟后再去从容解决。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aea668e6de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"64a7803525","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：《林彪元帅文集》（下册），香港凤凰书品， 2016年。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aea668e6de","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"681c1a5ae0","type":"paragraph","text":" \t（1967年5月5日）","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"aea668e6de","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}